  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We are investigating the chronic effect of daily assumption of Viagra on the blood vessels
      function in patients with impotence. The study will include 2 groups: 1- patients with
      multiple risk factors, e.g. hypertension 2- patients with no cardiovascular risk factors
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We are investigating the chronic effect of daily assumption of Viagra on the blood vessels
      function in patients with impotence. The study will include 2 groups: 1- patients with
      multiple risk factors, e.g. hypertension 2- patients with no cardiovascular risk factors
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
